[{},{"attrs":{"title":"webpack plugins","description":"How to add webpack plugins into my Nuxt.js application?"},"body":"<h1><a id=\"how-to-add-webpack-plugins-\" class=\"anchor\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"#how-to-add-webpack-plugins-\"><svg version=\"1.1\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"octicon octicon-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"/></svg></a>How to add webpack plugins?</h1><p>In your <code>nuxt.config.js</code> file:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs js\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">import</span> webpack <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">'webpack'</span>\n\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">default</span> {\n  <span class=\"hljs-attr\">build</span>: {\n    <span class=\"hljs-attr\">plugins</span>: [\n      <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">new</span> webpack.ProvidePlugin({\n        <span class=\"hljs-string\">'$'</span>: <span class=\"hljs-string\">'jquery'</span>,\n        <span class=\"hljs-string\">'_'</span>: <span class=\"hljs-string\">'lodash'</span>\n        <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// ...etc.</span>\n      })\n    ]\n  }\n}</code></pre>","docLink":"https://github.com/nuxt/docs/blob/master/en/faq/webpack-plugins.md"}]